gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Clippers 107, Mavericks 88
gameRecap.excerpt: The Clippers defeated the Mavericks, 107-88. Paul George recorded 25 points, nine rebounds, and four assists for the Clippers, while Russell Westbrook added 14 points, eight rebounds, and seven assists in the victory. Luka Doncic (30 points, four assists) and Kyrie Irving (26 points, six rebounds) combined for 56 points for the Mavericks in the losing effort. The Clippers improve to 7-8 on the season, while the Mavericks fall to 10-6.
